Class Summary

IntValueRequest Represents a request with an int value to pass to wiiuse API.
LedsRequest Represents a request to set leds of the wiimote with WiiUse API.
TwoIntValueRequest Represents a request with two int values to pass to wiiuse API.
WiiUseApiRequest Represents a request we could do to the WiiUse API.
